*Hot Burrito Chorus – backing vocals (track 11)

;Technical
* The Flying Burrito Brothers, Larry Marks, Henry Lewy – production
* Henry Lewy – engineer
* Tom Wilkes – art direction
* Barry Feinstein – cover photography

