<doc id="1138523" wikidata="Q1369207" url="?curid=1138523" title="Reika Hashimoto">
<text>is a Japanese model and actress. She is of Japanese-Spanish heritage. Her father is an American citizen of Spanish descent. She has been working as a model since she was 10, and her acting debut was in the 1999 movie &quot;Hakuchi&quot; (directed by Makoto Tezuka, opposite Tadanobu Asano), and has performed in several movies. On television, she had a participation on TV Asahi&#x27;s &quot;Profile&quot; and has performed in Chinese soap operas.

