==Twin towns – sister cities==

Saint-Dié-des-Vosges is twinned with:

* Arlon, Belgium (1962)
* Cattolica, Italy (1997)
* Crikvenica, Croatia (2006)
* Friedrichshafen, Germany (1973)
* Lorraine, Quebec, Canada (1990)
* Lowell, United States (1989)
* Meckhe, Senegal (1991)
* Zakopane, Poland (1990)
